# Package architecture

## Layer model
```
L5 — Embedded SDKs
   ↑ (consumed by targets)
L4 — Verification (orthogonal; reads L0-L3, writes verdicts)
   ↑
L3 — Orchestration
   ↑
L2 — Delegation & memory
   ↑
L1 — Coordination
   ↑
L0 — Foundations (no internal deps)
```

